The Puppy Owners Guide To Puppy Culture

In this guide, we outline the shared experiences and lessons that a Puppy Owner will benefit from when they follow the Puppy Culture program. Useful Information FOR PUPPY OWNERS FOR BREEDERS BREEDER PRINT-OUTS Reference sheets for Puppy Owners The puppy owners guide to Puppy Culture In this guide, we outline the shared experiences and lessons that a Puppy Owner will benefit from when they follow the Puppy Culture program. Download PDF Glossary of terms This quick start guide is intended to help demystify some of the terms that New Puppy Owners may come across as they explore the Puppy Culture suite of resources. Download PDF Essentials playlist This playlist is a guide through the film “Puppy Culture: The Powerful First 12 Weeks That Can Shape Your Puppy’s Future.” It will guide you through the chapters in the film that you want to focus on with your new puppy. Download PDF Product guide In this guide, we’ve collected together the products available within our Puppy Culture range that are more suited towards Puppy Owners. Download PDF Our social channels Our ever-growing Puppy Culture community is a unique place to ask questions, soak up the great wisdom others have to offer and to share your own experiences. Download PDF Is the Workbook suitable for Puppy Owners? The Workbook is a fantastic resource - packed with reference material, guidance, hints, tips, charts and worksheets - which acts as a companion product to the Original Puppy Culture film. However, with a focus on guiding you through (and recording), early litter developmental activities, it is probably more suited towards repeat Breeders than it is Puppy Owners. For Puppy Owners, a good alternative is to make use of theEssentials playlistor the Recap sections of the Original Puppy Culture film, in order to write a personalised outline plan for you and your puppy to follow.
